[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 1.4.1"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 1.4.1 are now fixed in
Tails 1.5.

We **strongly** encourage you to [[upgrade to
Tails 1.5|news/version_1.5]] as soon as possible.

